<plot>This is a touching account of the Somme battle and the horrors suffered by the men fighting. Gareth Myles plays a young soldier who deserts the trenches and goes on the run. He is pursued by fellow British soldiers and eventually shot. Back home his heavily pregnant wife receives the news and has to cope with the loss.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?494497</url></doc>
